00:11:41.660 --> 00:11:43.660
You know, Sam, the protest is serious.

00:11:43.660 --> 00:11:45.660
It's not all fun and games.

00:11:45.660 --> 00:11:47.660
Yeah, you know, maybe we should go with them.

00:11:47.660 --> 00:11:49.660
Come if you like, but not if you're just worried.

00:11:49.660 --> 00:11:50.660
We'll be fine.

00:11:50.660 --> 00:11:51.660
We will.

00:11:51.660 --> 00:11:52.660
Definitely.

00:11:52.660 --> 00:11:54.660
Okay, but you guys organize this thing,

00:11:54.660 --> 00:11:56.660
so you'll be responsible for everyone there.

00:11:56.660 --> 00:11:58.660
Yeah. You know, guys, just remember to use your common sense.

00:11:58.660 --> 00:12:00.660
I mean, that's the most important thing to keep in mind.

00:12:00.660 --> 00:12:02.660
I promise nothing will get out of hand.

00:12:02.660 --> 00:12:04.660
Okay. Well, all right. Hey, hey.

00:12:04.660 --> 00:12:06.660
Keep the things.

00:12:06.660 --> 00:12:08.660
Go for it. You got it.

00:12:08.660 --> 00:12:12.100
Well, Clarissa, let's just hope everything goes

00:12:12.100 --> 00:12:14.100
