00:13:13.580 --> 00:13:15.580
No, Sam. Your dad...

00:13:15.580 --> 00:13:18.580
Hey! Other people are waiting to use that phone.

00:13:18.580 --> 00:13:23.270
Okay. Sorry, sir.

00:13:23.270 --> 00:13:25.270
Okay, Sam. Here it goes.

00:13:25.270 --> 00:13:27.270
I mean, what's the worst they could say?

00:13:27.270 --> 00:13:29.270
I don't even want to think about it.

00:13:29.270 --> 00:13:33.830
Mom, it's me.

00:13:33.830 --> 00:13:35.830
Hey, you'll never guess where I'm calling from.

00:13:35.830 --> 00:13:46.600
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na...

00:13:46.600 --> 00:13:50.600
More Clarissa. More Snake, after this.

00:14:02.600 --> 00:14:06.840
Hey, they're taking on grown-ups from the rug up.

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:10.360
Call them bad, call them bold,

00:14:10.360 --> 00:14:13.600
